    "At the same time, the framework can index the data of direct access to outer space changes, and realize seamless integration with Pytorch and other neural network frameworks.",
    "For large-scale 3D sensing tasks such as point cloud voxel, scene reconstruction, non rigid point cloud registration (Jin et al., 2021; Dong et al., 2022), and volume deformation, researchers are allowed to complete the previous work with less code workload.",
